{
  "stem": "3964.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people came to me and said, well, do you remember I was friends of your mother and I was a friend of your father and I didn't know anything about it and we didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And nobody did anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody was guilty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In Germany there's a word, der Heinzelmaennchen, which means the-- the ghosts were responsible for what happened before 1938 and during 1938.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I had memories of what my father had told me, what my mother had told me, who was involved, directly involved, in our being treated the way we were treated.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At that particular time, American troops had moved into Gemunden as occupied territory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They stayed in a place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went to the captain, introduced myself to him, told him who I was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he introduced himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said he was working for-- with the CIC, counterintelligence corps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were looking for ex-Nazis if I could help them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I knew quite a few.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Since the town was little I knew most of them, if not all of them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I worked with the American Army for several months, hunting down these people who were Nazis and were actively involved or had been actively involved in hurting us, particularly us, or the Jews, and also other people who were decent German Christian people.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had an incident where I went on patrol with them into a town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we picked up a man who wanted to hitchhike.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I got into a conversation with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And somehow we got to talk about Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I brought up the subject, are there any Jews around?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There are no Jews around because Hitler killed them all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, did he kill 'em all?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
